{{Infobox book| |name =Jonah Hex: Shadows West |image =Jonahhexcover.gif |caption =Cover Art by '''[[Tim Truman]] and [[Sam Glanzman]]''' |author =[[Joe R. Lansdale]] |illustrator=Tim Truman, Sam Glanzman |cover_artist= |country =United States |language =English |series =[[Jonah Hex]] |genre =Western, [[Science Fiction]] |publisher =[[Vertigo (DC Comics)|Vertigo/DC Comics]] |pub_date =2014 |media_type =Full sized trade paperback |pages =389 |isbn =978-1-4012-4715-7 |preceded_by= |followed_by= }}
'''''Jonah Hex: Shadows West''''' is a collection of [[graphic novels]] written by American author [[Joe R. Lansdale]]. The artwork was done by writer and illustrator [[Timothy Truman]] and artist [[Sam Glanzman]]. These works were published from 1993 to 1999 by [[DC Comics]]. These all surround the adventures of fictional [[bounty hunter]] [[Jonah Hex]] who was originally created by writer [[John Albano]] and artist [[Tony DeZuniga]] in 1977. All of the original story and artwork has been redone and reprinted in high quality graphics by [[Vertigo (DC Comics)|Vertigo]]/[[DC Comics]] in 2014.<ref>{{cite web|last=DC Comics Review|title=Jonah Hex: Shadows West|url=http://www.dcuguide.com/JH/JHSW.php|accessdate=5 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Comic Shop.Com website|title=Jonah Hex: Shadows West|url=http://www.mycomicshop.com/search?TID=25431026|accessdate=5 April 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Jonah Hex|title=Jonah Hex Review|url=http://www.booklounge.ca/catalog/display.pperl?isbn=9781401247157&view=print|publisher=booklounge|accessdate=7 April 2014}}</ref>
