*'''[[wiktionary: peruse|peruse]]''' – read<ref name="auto5"/>
*'''PIN number''' – PIN<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=630}}: "redundant"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: place|place]]''' – put<ref name="auto5"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: portion|portion]]''' – part{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: possess|possess]]''' – have, own{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''point in time''', '''particular point in time''' – time, point, now, moment<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=640}}: "clumsy phrase"</ref>
*'''potentiality''' – potential<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=648}}: "jargon"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: practicable|practicable]]''' – 	practical{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: preclude|preclude]]''' – prevent{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''preowned''' – used<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=653}}: "euphemism"</ref>
*'''preliminary to''', '''[[wiktionary: previous|previous]] to''', '''[[wiktionary: previously|previously]]''', '''prior to''' – before{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=133}}<ref name="auto5"/><ref name="auto9"/><ref name="auto18"/>
*'''preparatory to''' – to prepare for{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=133}}<ref name="auto3"/>
*'''prior to''' – before {{cn|date=October 2017}}
*'''[[wiktionary: prioritize|prioritize]]''' – rank;{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}} set or make priorities{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=134}}
*'''[[wiktionary: proceed|proceed]]''' – do, go ahead, try{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto5"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: procure|procure]]''' – (omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: proficiency|proficiency]]''' – 	skill{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: promulgate|promulgate]]''' – issue, publish{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: provide|provide]]''' – give, offer, say{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''provided that''' – if{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=135}}<ref>{{harvnb|Schiess|2003-2004|pp=57–58}}: "wordy"</ref>
*'''provide guidance for''' – 	guide{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: purchase|purchase]]''' – buy{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto5"/><ref name="auto22">{{harvnb|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=11}}: "word to avoid"</ref>
*'''pursuant to''' – by, following, per, under;{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}} in response to, in carrying out, as required by<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2002|p=136}}: "legalese"</ref><ref name="auto6"/>

==Q==
*'''question as to whether''', '''question of whether''' – question whether{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=136}}
*'''quite puzzling''' – baffling<ref name="auto16"/>

==R==
*'''reason ... is because''' – because<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2002|pp=136–37}}: "verbose"</ref>
*'''refer back''' – refer<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2002|p=137}}: "redundan[t]"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: reflect|reflect]]''' – say, show{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''regard as being''' – regard as{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=137}}
*'''[[wiktionary: regarding|regarding]]''' – 	about, of, on{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto22"/>
*'''relative to''' – 	about, on{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: relocate|relocate]]''' – move{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: remain|remain]]''' – stay{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: remainder|remainder]]''' – 	rest{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: remuneration|remuneration]]''' – pay, payment{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: render|render]]''' – give, make{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: represents|represents]]''' – is{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: request|request]]''' – ask{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: require|require]]''' – must, need{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: requirement|requirement]]''' – need,{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}} rule{{sfn|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=26}}
*'''[[wiktionary: reside|reside]]''', '''[[wiktionary: residence|residence]]''' – live, house{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009b|p=91}}: "genteelism''</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: respectively|respectively]]''' – (omit){{sfn|SEC|1998|p=35}}
*'''[[wiktionary: retain|retain]]''' – keep{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: retire|retire]]''' – go to bed<ref name="auto5"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: rigorous|rigorous]]''' – harsh, rigid, severe{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}

==S==
*'''said, some, such, same''' – the, this, that{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2002|p=139}}: "legaldegook"</ref><ref name="auto6"/><ref name="auto"/><ref>{{harvnb|Schiess|2003-2004|p=56}}: "vague word"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: selection|selection]]''' – choice{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: separate|separate]]''' – ''After a number, this word is often unnecessary.''
*'''set forth in''' – in{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: shall|shall]]''' – must<ref name="auto20"/>{{sfn|Kimble|1992}}{{sfn|Schiess|2003-2004|p=74}}
*'''should you wish''' – if you want<ref name="auto22"/>
*'''similar to''' – like{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: solicit|solicit]]''' – ask for, request{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''state-of-the-art''' – latest{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: strategize|strategize]]''' – plan<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009b|p=91}}: "officialese"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: subject|subject]]''' – the, this, your{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: submit|submit]]''' – give, send{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: subsequent|subsequent]]''', '''[[wiktionary: subsequently|subsequently]]''', '''subsequent to''' – later, next, after, then{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}{{sfn|Garner|2002|p=141}}<ref name="auto5"/><ref name="auto9"/><ref name="auto18"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: substantial|substantial]]''' – large, much{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''successfully complete''' – complete, pass{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: sufficient|sufficient]]''' – enough{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto5"/>

==T==
*'''take action to''' – 	(omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: terminate|terminate]]''' – end, stop{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto14"/><ref name="auto22"/><ref name="auto15"/>
*'''than was formerly the case ''' – now<ref name="auto10"/>
*'''the month of''' – (omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''there are''' – (omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: therefore|therefore]]''' – thus, so{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto19"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: therein|therein]]''' – there{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''there is''' – 	(omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''the undersigned''' – I{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''the use of''' – (omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''this activity, command''' – us, we{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''[[wiktionary: timely|timely]]''' – prompt{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''time period''' – 	(either one){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''to be violative of''' – violate<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=845}}: "verbose"</ref>
*'''took advantage of''' – preyed<ref name="auto16"/>
*'''to wit''' – (omit)<ref>{{harvnb|Lebovitz|2001|p=56}}: "legalese"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: transpire|transpire]]''' (unless referring to plant [[transpiration]]) – happen<ref name="auto5"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: transmit|transmit]]''' – send{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto4"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: type|type]]''' – 	(omit){{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}

