*'''under the provisions of''' – under{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''until such time as''' – until{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto7"/>
*'''utilize, utilization''' – use{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto14"/><ref name="auto4"/><ref name="auto15"/>

==V==
*'''[[wiktionary: validate|validate]]''' – confirm{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}	
*'''variation''' – change{{sfn|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=30}}
*'''various different''' – "various" or "different"<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=838}}: "redundant"</ref>
*'''very''' – (omit)<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2009a|p=842}}: "weasel word"</ref>
*'''[[wiktionary: viable|viable]]''' – practical, workable{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}

==W==
*'''[[wiktionary: warrant|warrant]]''' – call for, permit{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''we are in receipt of''' – we've received<ref name="auto6"/><ref name="auto3"/>
*'''[[wiktionary: whereas|whereas]]''' – because, since{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''whether or not''' – whether,{{sfn|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=31}} if
*'''[[whosoever]]''', '''[[whomsoever]]''' – whoever, whomever<ref>{{harvnb|Garner|2002|p=147}}: "legalese"</ref>
*'''with a view to''' – by, from<ref name="auto18"/>
*'''with reference to''', '''with regard to''' – about{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}<ref name="auto18"/>
*'''with respect to''' – on, about<ref name="auto18"/>
*'''with the exception of''' – 	except for{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}
*'''with the minimum of delay''' – quickly (or say when){{sfn|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=31}}
*'''[[wiktionary: witnessed|witnessed]]''' – saw{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}

==Y==
*'''you are requested''' – please{{sfn|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=32}}
*'''your attention is drawn''' – please see, please note{{sfn|Plain English Campaign|2001|p=32}}
*'''your office''' – you{{sfn|Simple word suggestions|2013}}

